<view class="page cancel-handle-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">处理取消协商申请</view><view class="form-header-desc">车商客户已对该订单发起取消协商申请，请审核处理。</view></view><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="section request-card"><view class="request-meta"><text class="req-label">发起时间:</text><text class="req-value">{{b}}</text></view><view class="request-reason-block"><text class="label">车商取消原因:</text><view class="reason-text-box">{{c}}</view></view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">处理意见</view><view class="field"><block wx:if="{{r0}}"><textarea class="textarea remark-textarea" placeholder="可填写同意或拒绝的具体理由/说明..." placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" maxlength="150" value="{{d}}" bindinput="{{e}}"/></block><view class="word-counter">{{f}} / 150 字</view></view></view><view class="fixed-footer button-row"><button class="danger-btn flex-1 animate-btn" loading="{{g}}" bindtap="{{h}}"> 拒绝取消申请 </button><button class="primary-btn flex-1 animate-btn" loading="{{i}}" bindtap="{{j}}"> 同意取消订单 </button></view></view>